  "texts": [
    "It fully reflects that the PINNs-e-RGCN model is characterized by less required data and high accuracy.",
    "(3) Compared to conventional systems, this system is able to handle given tasks quickly and efficiently with high application versatility.",
    "There are a lot of elevator data, and this paper only uses vibration data for research.",
    "So more data types (such as electrical signals, image data, etc.)",
    "will be introduced afterwards."
